  • Package pt.uc.dei.entities

    • Class pt.uc.dei.entities.ActivationTokenEntity

      class ActivationTokenEntity extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • creationDate
          LocalDateTime creationDate
          The timestamp when this token was created.

          Used to determine token expiration and for auditing purposes.

        • id
          Long id
          The unique identifier for the activation token.

          Automatically generated by the database.

        • temporaryUser
          TemporaryUserEntity temporaryUser
          The temporary user account associated with this activation token.

          Nullable to allow for token pre-generation scenarios. Indexed for efficient user-token queries.

        • tokenValue
          String tokenValue
          The unique token string used for account activation.

          Stored as a cryptographically secure random value. Indexed for fast lookup and uniqueness.

    • Class pt.uc.dei.entities.AppraisalEntity

      class AppraisalEntity extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • appraisedUser
          UserEntity appraisedUser
          The user being appraised.

          Many-to-one relationship with UserEntity. Indexed for fast lookup.

        • appraisingUser
          UserEntity appraisingUser
          The user performing the appraisal (manager).

          Many-to-one relationship with UserEntity. Indexed for fast lookup.

        • creationDate
          LocalDate creationDate
          The date when the appraisal was created.

          Cannot be updated once set. Used for sorting and filtering.

        • cycle
          CycleEntity cycle
          The cycle in which this appraisal occurs.

          Many-to-one relationship with CycleEntity. Indexed for efficient retrieval.

        • editedDate
          LocalDate editedDate
          The date when the appraisal was last edited.

          Can be updated to reflect the latest modification.

        • feedback
          String feedback
          The feedback provided during the appraisal.

          Optional and can be updated. Used for qualitative assessment.

        • id
          Long id
          The unique identifier for the appraisal.

          Generated automatically by the database.

        • score
          Integer score
          The score assigned in the appraisal.

          Optional and can be updated. Used for performance evaluation.

        • state
          AppraisalState state
          The current state of the appraisal (e.g., IN_PROGRESS, COMPLETED).

          Used for filtering and workflow management. Indexed for fast filtering.

        • submissionDate
          LocalDate submissionDate
          The date when the appraisal was submitted.

          Optional. Used to track when the appraisal was finalized.

    • Class pt.uc.dei.entities.TemporaryUserEntity

      class TemporaryUserEntity extends Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • activationToken
          ActivationTokenEntity activationToken
          Activation token associated with this temporary account.

          Features: - Bi-directional one-to-one mapping - Automatic cascade operations - Orphan removal when temporary user is deleted

        • email
          String email
          User's email address for account verification.

          Maximum length of 254 characters (RFC 5321 compliant). Marked as unique to prevent duplicate registrations.

        • id
          Long id
          Unique database identifier for the temporary account. Auto-incremented by the database.
        • password
          String password
          Encrypted password for the temporary account.

          Should be hashed using secure algorithm before storage.

        • secretKey
          String secretKey
